These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, cat, lizard
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the pony and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Pet      | lizard | mouse | cat   | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
House: art-deco, farmhouse, ranch-style, tower
1. the tower house is between the person who's hobby is reading and the farmhouse house##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| House   | farmhouse    | tower   | art-deco | ranch-style       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, r&b, d&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the fan of r&b is between the fan of gospel and the person eating corn##2
3. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | r&b   | d&b | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, davidoff, aristoff, bluemaster
1. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the chaman-smoker and the owner of the rat##2
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Cigar   | aristoff | bluemaster | chaman | davidoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, dog, rabbit
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Pet      | dog | horse  | rabbit | hedgehog    |

