.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, spy, crime, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rowing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching spy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime           | musical | thriller  |
| Sport         | cycling | skateboarding | parkour   | rowing |

