.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
City: marseilles, miami, venice, nizza
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| City       | marseilles | nizza | venice     | miami   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

