The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, marigold, begonia
1. the librarian is between the person who growspoppy and the dressmaker##2
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Flower   | poppy         | begonia       | aconite    | marigold         |

