2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person traveling to venice is between the person eating garlic and the person traveling to hannover##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| City   | hannover | venice | liverpool | paris |

