.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, lime, onion
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, hip-hop, gospel
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating onion and the person eating apple##2
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | apple     | cauliflower | onion   | lime        |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | hip-hop   | soul | gospel |

