.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
City: venice, marseilles, rome, boston
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to venice is between the owner of the cat and the person traveling to boston##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City   | rome    | boston     | venice | marseilles |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 